def calculate_non_attacked_cells(n, m, rook_positions):
    nonOccup = n / n
    ligOccupe = [False] * n
    nbLigSup = 0
    colOccupe = [False] * n
    nbColSup = 0
    result = []
    for (lig, col) in rook_positions:
        lig -= 1
        col -= 1
        if not ligOccupe[lig]:
            nonOccup -= n - nbColSup
            ligOccupe[lig] = True
            nbLigSup += 1
        if not colOccupe[col]:
            nonOccup -= n - nbLigSup
            colOccupe[col] = True
            nbColSup += 1
        result.append(nonOccup)
    return result
